<html>

<head>
	<title>Pixi Hotwire</title>

	<meta id="viewport" name="viewport"
		content="width=device-width, minimum-scale=1.0, initial-scale=1.0, maximum-scale=1.0, user-scalable=no, shrink-to-fit=no, viewport-fit=cover" />
	<meta name="apple-mobile-web-app-capable" content="yes">


	<style>
		html,
		body {
			margin: 0;
			padding: 0;
			height: 100%;
			overflow: hidden;
		}

		#pixi-content {
			background: #000000;
			width: 100%;
			height: 100%;
		}

		.toggle {
			margin: 0 0 0 2rem;
			position: relative;
			display: inline-block;
			width: 3rem;
			height: 1.7rem;
		}

		.toggle input {
			display: none;
		}

		.roundbutton {
			position: absolute;
			top: 0;
			left: 0;
			bottom: 0;
			right: 0;
			width: 100%;
			background-color: #5c6269;
			
			display: block;
			transition: all 0.3s;
			border-radius: 1.7rem;
			cursor: pointer;
		}

		.roundbutton:before {
			position: absolute;
			content: "";
			height: 1.2rem;
			width: 1.25rem;
			border-radius: 100%;
			display: block;
			left: 0.25rem;
			bottom: 0.25rem;
			background-color: white;
			transition: all 0.3s;
		}

		input:checked+.roundbutton {
			background-color: #1f9208;
		}

		input:checked+.roundbutton:before {
			transform: translate(1.3rem, 0);
		}
	</style>

</head>
<body>
	<noscript>Please enable JavaScript in your web browser to view this page.</noscript>
	
	<div style="display: flex; padding-left: 10px; padding-right: 10px;">
		<div>
			<span id="renderfps"></span> |
			<span id="animationfps"></span>
			<span>....................................................</span>
			<h3>General Settings</h3>
			<label for="animationsetting">Animation:</label>
			<input type="number" id="animationsetting" name="animationsetting" min="0" max="60" value="60"><br><br>
			<label for="rendersetting">Render:</label>
			<input type="number" id="rendersetting" name="rendersetting" min="0" max="60" value="60"><br><br>
			<div style="display: flex; align-items: center;">
				<span style="margin-top: 1px;">Pause Game</span>
				<label class="toggle">
					<input id="pausegame" type="checkbox">
					<span class="roundbutton"></span>
				</label>
			</div>
			<h3>Particle Dynamics</h3>
			<div style="display: flex; align-items: center;">
				<span style="margin-top: 1px;">Forcefield</span>
				<label class="toggle">
					<input id="forcefield" type="checkbox">
					<span class="roundbutton"></span>
				</label>
			</div><br>
			<div style="display: flex; align-items: center;">
				<span style="margin-top: 1px;">Trajectory</span>
				<label class="toggle">
					<input id="trajectory" type="checkbox">
					<span class="roundbutton"></span>
				</label>
			</div><br>
			<label for="method">Method:</label>
			<select name="method" id="method">
				<option value=0>RungeKutta</option>
				<option value=1>Euler</option>
			</select>
			<h3>Hierarchical Transform.</h3>
			<div>
				<label for="hierarchicalslider">Radius:</label>
				<input type="range" min="-50" max="50" value="0" id="hierarchicalslider">
			</div>
			<h3>Path Interpolation</h3>
			<div style="display: flex; align-items: center;">
				<span style="margin-top: 1px;">Splines Path</span>
				<label class="toggle">
					<input id="splines" type="checkbox">
					<span class="roundbutton"></span>
				</label>
			</div><br>
			<div style="display: flex; align-items: center;">
				<span style="margin-top: 1px;">Spline Speed</span>
				<label class="toggle">
					<input id="splinesspeed" type="checkbox">
					<span class="roundbutton"></span>
				</label>
			</div>
			<h3>Voronoi</h3>
			<div style="display: flex; align-items: center;">
				<span style="margin-top: 1px;">Distance Field</span>
				<label class="toggle">
					<input id="distancefield" type="checkbox">
					<span class="roundbutton"></span>
				</label>
			</div><br>
			<h3>Points and Lifes</h3>
			<label for="pointlabel">Points:</label>
			<span id="pointoutput"></span>
			<br>
			<label for="lifelabel">Lifes:</label>
			<span id="lifeoutput"></span>
			<h3>Instructions</h3>
			<br>
			<label for="manual">In order to win you need to launch Celli through the evil viruses. Celli has three lives and needs to get to the other side of the screen a total of five times to win.
				Just click near the catapult and launch Celli to victory.
			</label>
		</div>
		<div id="pixi-content"><canvas id="pixi-canvas" /></div>
	</div>
	
</body>
</html>